Private Function RandomString(size As Integer, lowerCase As Boolean) As String Dim builder As New system.Text.StringBuilder() Dim random As New Random() Dim ch As Char Dim i As Integer For i = 0 To size - 1 ch = Convert.ToChar(Convert.ToInt32((26 * random.NextDouble() + 65))) builder.Append(ch) Next If lowerCase Then Return builder.ToString().ToLower() End If Return builder.ToString() End Function 'RandomString
